<p>I'm using <a href="http://tarruda.github.io/bootstrap-datetimepicker/" rel="nofollow">http://tarruda.github.io/bootstrap-datetimepicker/</a> library for date picking.</p>  <p>My code is jsp file is:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;div id="endDate" class="input-append date"&gt; &lt;input id="input_endDate" name="endDate" data-format="yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm:ss" type="text"/&gt; &lt;span class="add-on"&gt;     &lt;i data-time-icon="icon-time" data-date-icon="icon-calendar" &gt;     &lt;/i&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;/div&gt; </code></pre>  <p>I set value to this date and time field in js file:</p>  <pre><code>$('#input_endDate').val('2015-10-02 13:25:31'); </code></pre>  <p>The problem is when I click to calendar button the input field get current date and time. But I want that calendar will show the date from my input field when I click to calendar button</p>